<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="26Apr1929"><font color="red">26 April 1929</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am working night, noon and morning. C.K. Ogden is doing the preface &hellip; You will scarcely recognise my fables now &hellip; I was awake nearly all last night trying to solve  a problem in elementary mathematics &mdash; all this for a word or two. </div>
